<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="logoBlack.png" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Rachell Skinner - Data-Driven Works</title>
		<!--Bootstrap Stylesheet -->
		<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
	</head>
	<body>
	<header>
        <Header />
	</header>
    <br>

    <div class="container">

		<!--Project 1 -->
		<div class="row">
			<!-- Project Preview Column -->
			<div class="col-md-7 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center vh-100" style="background-image: url('/blob4.png'); background-size: contain; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
				<video class="d-block mx-auto w-100 img-fluid" width="794" height="516" playsinline autoplay loop muted>
					<source src="/projectPreviews/workingChantsPreview.mp4" type="video/mp4">
					Your browser does not support the video tag.
				</video>
			</div>
			<!-- Project Preview Column -->

			<!-- Text Column -->
			<div class="col-md-5 my-auto px-5">
				<h1 class="previewHTxt">Working Chants - ArcGIS Story Map</h1>
				<p class="previewPTxt">Working Chants explores Coastal Carolina University’s student job landscape using personally obtained data from 42 survey respondents. Accompanied by data tools like Voyant Tools and Tableau for visual graphics portraying the data found from student workers’ experiences. These findings resulted in an overall satisfactory working experience depending on the department, pay, and management presented using ArcGIS story maps.</p>
				
				<!-- Button -->
				<div class="d-grid gap-2 col-md-8 mx-auto py-3">
					<a class="btn btn-outline-primary button" href="https://storymaps.com/stories/fb691f830d5941ca86a7328cf3b988ed" target="_blank">View Live Site</a>
				</div>
				<!-- Button END -->
			</div>
			<!-- Text Column END-->
		</div>
		<!--Project 1 END -->
		<br>

		<!--Project 2 -->
		<div class="row">
			<!-- Project Preview Column -->
			<div class="col-md-7 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center vh-100" style="background-image: url('/blob5.png'); background-size: contain; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
				<video class="d-block mx-auto w-100 img-fluid" width="794" height="516" playsinline autoplay loop muted>
					<source src="/projectPreviews/swayAuthenticityPreview.mp4" type="video/mp4">
					Your browser does not support the video tag.
				</video>
			</div>
			<!-- Project Preview Column -->

			<!-- Text Column -->
			<div class="col-md-5 my-auto px-5">
				<h1 class="previewHTxt">Authenticity & Genuineness From a Jennifer Egan Perspective - Microsoft Sway</h1>
				<p class="previewPTxt">Authenticity & Genuineness From a Jennifer Egan Perspective examines the larger topic of authenticity among GoodReads and Amazon book reviewers in Jennifer Egan’s novels, <em>A Visit From the Goon Squad</em> (2010), and its sequel, <em>The Candy House</em> (2022). An 80s web of connection experience leading into a sci-fi future dystopia using Mallet text-mining and Voyant Tools text analysis to discover new interpretations presented with Microsoft Sway.</p>
				
				<!-- Button -->
				<div class="d-grid gap-2 col-md-8 mx-auto py-3">
					<a class="btn btn-outline-primary button" href="https://sway.cloud.microsoft/eVxfkeh6tqJmFPKS?ref=Link" target="_blank" download>View Live Site</a>
				</div>
				<!-- Button END -->
			</div>
			<!-- Text Column END-->
		</div>
		<!--Project 2 END -->
		<br>

		<!--Project 3 -->
		<div class="row">
			<!-- Project Preview Column -->
			<div class="col-md-7 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center vh-100" style="background-image: url('/blob6.png'); background-size: contain; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
				<video class="d-block mx-auto w-100 img-fluid" width="794" height="516" playsinline autoplay loop muted>
					<source src="/projectPreviews/peopleAbortionsPreview.mp4" type="video/mp4">
					Your browser does not support the video tag.
				</video>
			</div>
			<!-- Project Preview Column -->

			<!-- Text Column -->
			<div class="col-md-5 my-auto px-5">
				<h1 class="previewHTxt">People & Abortions - Presentation</h1>
				<p class="previewPTxt">From an intersectionality perspective, People & Abortions discusses Roe v. Wade including the overturn in 2022 and the effects it has on various people including marginalized groups, and the potential consequences. Created in Canva, this presentation draws from recent abortion statistics and social media discussions to reflect on our personal privileges and actions.</p>
				
				<!-- Button -->
				<div class="d-grid gap-2 col-md-8 mx-auto py-3">
					<a class="btn btn-outline-primary button" href="https://www.canva.com/design/DAFarE-Jp_c/2DlKKSdKneVL8u2abCarUQ/edit?utm_content=DAFarE-Jp_c&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link2&utm_source=sharebutton" target="_blank">View Presentation</a>
				</div>
				<!-- Button END -->
			</div>
			<!-- Text Column END-->
		</div>
		<!--Project 3 END -->


        
		<!--Next/Last Page Button -->
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row justify-content-md-center justify-content-md-between align-items-center">
			  <div class="col-md-6 mb-3 mb-md-0 text-center text-md-start">
				<h2 class="nextProjectsLinks">
				  <a href="/programming-works" class="text-decoration-none">
					<img class="icon" src="/arrow-left-short.svg" alt="Left Arrow Icon SVG">
					Last: Programming Works
				  </a>
				</h2>
			  </div>
			  <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-end">
				<h2 class="nextProjectsLinks">
				  <a href="/design-driven-works" class="text-decoration-none">
					Next: Design-Driven Works
					<img class="icon" src="/arrow-right-short.svg" alt="Right Arrow Icon SVG">
				  </a>
				</h2>
			  </div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--Next/Last Page Button END -->
    </div>
	
    <br>
    <Footer />
	</body>
